sentences.sentence: Ramsauer told the daily Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung on Wednesday that studies have shown slow classical music has a calming effect on people.
sentences.translation: 拉姆·绍尔周三对《法兰克福广讯报》说，研究显示缓慢的古典音乐对人们有镇静作用。
